---
import Layout from '../../../layouts/Layout.astro';
const lang = 'en' as const;
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy of SUZUKI ENTERPRISE CO., LTD." lang={lang}>
  <section class="py-20 max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <h1 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-bold border-l-4 border-accent-400 pl-3 mb-2 text-brand-900">
      Privacy Policy
    </h1>
    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mb-10 ml-1">プライバシーポリシー</p>

    <div class="prose-jp">
      <p>SUZUKI ENTERPRISE CO., LTD. (hereinafter "the Company") recognizes the protection of your personal information as an important responsibility, and complies with the Act on the Protection of Personal Information and other related laws.</p>

      <h2>1. Purpose of Use</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Responding to inquiries and document requests</li>
        <li>Providing product proposals and quotations</li>
        <li>Communicating regarding contracts</li>
        <li>Recruitment</li>
        <li>Service improvement and new service development</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>2. Third-Party Disclosure</h2>
      <p>We do not disclose personal information to third parties without consent, except as required by law.</p>

      <h2>3. Cookies</h2>
      <p>Cookies are small text files stored in your browser when you visit a website. This site uses the following cookies and similar technologies for usage analysis and service improvement:</p>
      <table>
        <thead>
          <tr><th>Type</th><th>Purpose</th><th>Provider</th></tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Essential</td><td>Basic site functionality</td><td>The Company</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Analytics</td><td>Usage tracking and improvement</td><td>Google Analytics 4</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
      <p>You can accept or decline cookies through your browser settings. Disabling cookies may affect some site functionality.</p>
      <p>For third-party privacy policies, please refer to:</p>
      <ul>
        <li>
          <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
            Google Privacy Policy
          </a>
        </li>
      </ul>

      <h2>4. Contact</h2>
      <p>SUZUKI ENTERPRISE CO., LTD.<br />Suzuki Bldg. 3F, 2-2-34 Kizuki, Nakahara-ku, Kawasaki, Kanagawa 211-0025, JAPAN<br />TEL: +81-44-433-6399</p>

      <p class="text-right text-sm text-slate-500 mt-8">Last revised: May 6, 2026</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
